ACCELEROMETER

static final java.lang.String ACCELEROMETER
Constant defining the sensor type Accelerometer. Sensor data is sent as an array of 3 float values representing the acceleration on the x-axis, y-axis and z-axis respectively. All values are in SI units (m/s^2) For more information about the accelerometer sensor type, see android.hardware.Sensor#TYPE_ACCELEROMETER

1.0
